  "prompt": "Which one is better: Royal Enfield Standard 350 or Classic 350?",
  "response": "The choice between the Royal Enfield Standard 350 and the Classic 350 depends on your personal preferences and intended use. Here are some key differences and considerations to help you decide which one might be better for you:\n\n### Royal Enfield Standard 350:\n\n**Pros:**\n- **Minimalist Design:** The Standard 350 features a more stripped-down and classic design, appealing to those who prefer a raw, retro look.\n- **Lightweight Handling:** Generally, the Standard version may be a bit lighter, offering slightly more agile handling, especially in urban environments.\n- **Price:** It may be priced lower than the Classic variant, making it a more economical choice.\n\n**Cons:**\n- **Fewer Features:** The Standard 350 might come with fewer modern features and comforts compared to the Classic model.\n\n### Royal Enfield Classic 350:\n\n**Pros:**\n- **Retro Styling:** The Classic 350 is known for its vintage-inspired design and aesthetics, which may appeal to riders looking for a more styled motorcycle.\n- **Comfort:** Usually offers a more comfortable riding position and seat, making it suitable for longer rides.\n- **Modern Features:** The Classic 350 often includes more modern features and upgraded components, enhancing the overall riding experience.\n\n**Cons:**\n- **Weight:** May be heavier compared to the Standard 350, which can affect maneuverability in tight spaces.\n- **Price:** Typically, it may come at a higher price point due to the enhanced features and styling.\n\n### Conclusion:\n\nIf you prefer a more minimalist and potentially lighter motorcycle, the Royal Enfield Standard 350 might be the better choice for you. On the other hand, if you favor vintage aesthetics combined with more comfort and modern features, the Classic 350 would likely be the better option. Consider your riding style, preference for design, and intended use when making your decision. Test riding both models, if possible, can also help you make the best choice for your needs.",
